date_time_attributes__v_model_descriptio: binding value, if it is an array, the length should be 2
date_time_attributes__date_format_descri: format is designed to display the date in the input data.
date_time_attributes__time_format_descri: format is for displaying the time in the time input (ie in datetime, datetimerange modes)
date_time_attributes__combine_formats_de: generate the format for the picker from the date-format & time-format props
date_time_attributes__type_description: which type of picker should be displayed
date_time_attributes__mode_description: in which mode you want to display the calendar.
date_time_attributes__first_day_of_week_: the order of the days of the week in the day calendar
date_time_attributes__weekday_format_des: format of the days of the week displayed in the calendar
date_time_attributes__month_cell_format_: format of months displayed in the calendar
date_time_attributes__month_button_forma: the format of the month, which is displayed in the button located in the top panel of the calendar
date_time_attributes__shortcuts_descript: list of shortcuts to quickly select a date
date_time_attributes__default_time_descr: the time that will be set by default. The expected format is “00:00:00”.
date_time_attributes__locale_description: the language in which you want to display data in the picker. (Use only if you do not have the vue-i18n package)
date_time_attributes__disabled_date_desc: the option is used to define blocked dates
